Package org.shingo.shingoeventsapp.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OnTaskComplete
    This interface is used as callback for android.os.AsyncTask.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GetAsyncData
    This class is used to make an asynchronous call to the API to fetch data.
    InitLoader
    This class is used to load all of the data for Agendas, Affiliates, Exhibitors, Recipients Sessions, Speakers, and Sponsors.
    RestApi
    A central object to store needed data and return an initialized AsyncTask
